name: Agrona Generative
description:
Agrona Generative: 

Introducing the major players within the ranks of Generatives and Disruptives at Gormenghast.

Agrona G is a hardened battle-star on the side of ‘The Generatives’; though the Generatives do not have a form of hierarchical systems in place within their society, preferring to recognise all as equal, there are individuals within the collective that stand out and shine.

And shine Agrona G does.

Agrona G is an established deep player of concern. The remnants of previous generative construct attached to AG’s timeline read like a Generative warriors dictionary.

No other generative can hold a candle to AG’s strict warrior code and you will see AG performing major roles time and again throughout the history of Generatives and Disruptives at Gormenghast.

This is a story-line you do not want to miss - extremely powerful players have now entered the fray.


PNG 4800 x 4800 || December 11th 2021 || Dark Art digital painting – expanding the Gormenghast universe
